          source(media='(min-width:10px)' srcset='/images/slider/6-mobile.jpg' type='image/jpeg')
          img(src='/images/slider/6.jpg')
    .swiper-pagination
    .swiper-button-prev
    .swiper-button-next

  .container#dining
    h2 Dining
    .split-container
      .split
        p Private dining, corporate booking and takeaways like you have never experienced before. 
        p We are rooted in the belief that food never has to be boring and that flavour is for everyone. That’s why we have developed a mighty combination of offerings so that we can offer you amazing food whether it’s a date night, a 40th anniversary or something to schmooze your staff with.
      .split
        p Explore our Feasted packages and get in touch with ideas and inspiration for your next event. 
        a.button.button-primary.scroll(href='/contact') Enquire Now
    .products
      .product
        img(src='/images/dining/mexi-hohoho/4.jpg')
        .product-description
          h4 
            a(href='/dining/mexi-hohoho') Mexi-Ho Ho Ho
          p.small Mexi-Ho Ho Ho puts a Feasted twist on a classic Christmas dinner, packed full of flavour.  
          p.small Festivities will look different for 2020 but whether you get to bundle around one table with your loved ones or you will have to get a little more creative this Christmas, our food will be there for you all to enjoy. 
          a(href='/dining/mexi-hohoho') Read more...
      .product
        img(src='/images/dining/board/1.jpg')
        .product-description
          h4 
            a(href='/dining/board') BOARD
          p.small We’ve created seasonal takeaway boards that boast bold favours and gorgeous combinations. Bookable for occasions or ‘just because’ this isn’t your average takeaway and we work with local farmers and creatives to use ingredients that are rich and readily available, supporting other businesses as well as bringing you amazing food. 
          a(href='/dining/board') Read more...
      .product
        img(src='/images/dining/once-upon-a-plate/1.jpg')
        .product-description
          h4 
            a(href='/dining/once-upon-a-plate') Once Upon A Plate
          p.small Gather your friends, gather your family and sit back for an evening of indulgence and magic. 
          p.small Once upon a Plate is a private dining experience like no other. We work with you to learn about your event or occasion and note the stories and tales that you tell us around your attendees. We will weave this into the story of the food, creating a totally bespoke menu for you and your guests. 
          a(href='/dining/once-upon-a-plate') Read more...
      .product
        img(src='/images/dining/corporate/6.jpg')
        .product-description
          h4 
            a(href='/dining/corporate-team-building') Corporate
          p.small Available for up to thirty people, we cater for your team in a different kind of way.
          p.small Busting boredom and cooking up the tastiest of creations, we can set up kitchen in your workspace or we have a range of kitchens that we can book for the activity.
          a(href='/dining/corporate-team-building') Read more...
      
  #education   
    .container
      h2 Education
      .split-container
        .split
          p With a background in education as well as creating amazing food, a core part of what we do is teaching others to do the same. We work with employers, schools and further education providers both locally, here in Stoke, and across the country.
          p We're all about great flavour and using skills like maths and science in both everyday and extraordinary cooking. 
          a.button.button-primary.scroll(href='/contact') Enquire Now
        .split
          .product.product__full-width
            img(src='/images/education/stoke-on-trent-college/2.jpg')
            .product-description
              h4 
                a(href='/education/stoke-on-trent-college') Stoke-on-Trent College
              p.small We’ve partnered with Stoke-on-Trent College to bring an all-new Level 3 qualification in Gastronomy to the college. 
              p.small Consultancy projects include FE college or high school  course creation, teacher training and restaurant menus. 
              a(href='/education/stoke-on-trent-college') Read more...
